### 学成在线 - 课程管理模块 HTTP 测试
### 使用方式：IntelliJ IDEA 打开本文件，点击 "Run all requests" 一键执行全部用例
### VS Code：安装 REST Client 扩展，可逐条发送或使用脚本批量执行
### 前置：服务运行于 http://localhost:11001，数据库已执行 xcplus_content.sql
### 一键自动化：cd http && python run-tests.py

@baseUrl = http://localhost:11001/content
@companyId = 1
@companyId2 = 2
### 机构归属：课程1-15属机构1，课程16-22属机构2

###############################################################################
# 一、课程分类
###############################################################################

### 1.1 获取分类树（成功，无需 X-Company-Id）
GET {{baseUrl}}/course-categories/tree

###############################################################################
# 二、课程管理 - 分页查询
###############################################################################

### 2.1 分页-无条件（成功）
POST {{baseUrl}}/courses/page
Content-Type: application/json
X-Company-Id: {{companyId}}

{
  "pageNo": 1,
  "pageSize": 10
}

### 2.2 分页-按名称（成功）
POST {{baseUrl}}/courses/page
Content-Type: application/json
X-Company-Id: {{companyId}}

{
  "pageNo": 1,
  "pageSize": 10,
  "courseName": "Java"
}

### 2.3 分页-按审核状态（成功）
POST {{baseUrl}}/courses/page
Content-Type: application/json
X-Company-Id: {{companyId}}

{
  "pageNo": 1,
  "pageSize": 10,
  "auditStatus": "202004"
}

### 2.4 分页-按发布状态且 pageSize=2（验证分页生效）
POST {{baseUrl}}/courses/page
Content-Type: application/json
X-Company-Id: {{companyId}}

{
  "pageNo": 1,
  "pageSize": 2,
  "publishStatus": "203002"
}

### 2.5 分页-组合条件（成功）
POST {{baseUrl}}/courses/page
Content-Type: application/json
X-Company-Id: {{companyId}}

{
  "pageNo": 1,
  "pageSize": 5,
  "courseName": "AI",
  "auditStatus": "202004",
  "publishStatus": "203002"
}

### 2.6 分页-GET 方式
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses?pageNo=1&pageSize=10
X-Company-Id: {{companyId}}

###############################################################################
# 三、课程 CRUD
###############################################################################

### 3.1 新增课程（成功）
POST {{baseUrl}}/courses
Content-Type: application/json
X-Company-Id: {{companyId}}

{
  "name": "接口测试新增课程",
  "users": "测试学员",
  "tags": "测试,接口",
  "mt": "1-001-001",
  "st": "1-001-001",
  "grade": "204001",
  "teachMode": "200001",
  "description": "用于接口测试的课程",
  "pic": null
}

### 3.2 新增课程-失败-名称为空
POST {{baseUrl}}/courses
Content-Type: application/json
X-Company-Id: {{companyId}}

{
  "name": "",
  "users": "测试学员",
  "tags": "测试",
  "mt": "1-001-001",
  "st": "1-001-001",
  "grade": "204001",
  "teachMode": "200001",
  "description": "名称为空应失败",
  "pic": null
}

### 3.3 新增课程-失败-必填缺失
POST {{baseUrl}}/courses
Content-Type: application/json
X-Company-Id: {{companyId}}

{
  "users": "测试学员",
  "tags": "测试",
  "mt": "1-001-001",
  "st": "1-001-001",
  "grade": "204001",
  "teachMode": "200001"
}

### 3.4 获取课程详情（成功）
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/1
X-Company-Id: {{companyId}}

### 3.5 获取课程详情-失败-不存在
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/99999
X-Company-Id: {{companyId}}

### 3.6 获取课程详情-失败-越权（课程16属机构2）
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/16
X-Company-Id: 1

### 3.7 更新课程（成功）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/courses/1
Content-Type: application/json
X-Company-Id: {{companyId}}

{
  "name": "Java核心技术从入门到精通（已更新）",
  "users": "零基础学员、转行开发者",
  "tags": "Java,后端,Spring",
  "mt": "1-001-001",
  "st": "1-001-001",
  "grade": "204001",
  "teachMode": "200001",
  "description": "更新后的课程介绍",
  "pic": null
}

### 3.8 更新课程-失败-名称为空
PUT {{baseUrl}}/courses/1
Content-Type: application/json
X-Company-Id: {{companyId}}

{
  "name": "",
  "users": "测试",
  "tags": "测试",
  "mt": "1-001-001",
  "st": "1-001-001",
  "grade": "204001",
  "teachMode": "200001"
}

### 3.9 删除课程（成功，建议用机构2的课程22）
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/courses/22
X-Company-Id: 2

### 3.10 删除课程-失败-越权
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/courses/1
X-Company-Id: 2

