###############################################################################
# 九、完整流程（与 run-tests.py 一致，按顺序执行）
# 流程：列表→查id→新增→更新→再查id→删除→再列表 + 各模块越权
# 说明：9.4/9.14/9.29 新增后需将返回的 id 手动替换下方 {{newId}}/{{newTid}}/{{newPid}}
# 一键自动化：python run-tests.py（无需手动替换）
###############################################################################

### 9.1 分类树
GET {{baseUrl}}/course-categories/tree

### 9.2 课程-列表
POST {{baseUrl}}/courses/page
Content-Type: application/json
X-Company-Id: {{companyId}}
{"pageNo":1,"pageSize":5}

### 9.3 课程-查id1
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/1
X-Company-Id: {{companyId}}

### 9.4 课程-新增（记下返回的 id 用于后续更新/删除）
POST {{baseUrl}}/courses
Content-Type: application/json
X-Company-Id: {{companyId}}
{"name":"流程测试课程","users":"测试","tags":"测试","mt":"1-001-001","st":"1-001-001","grade":"204001","teachMode":"200001","description":"流程测试"}

### 9.5 课程-更新（将上一步返回的 id 替换下方 /courses/{{newId}}）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/courses/{{newId}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Company-Id: {{companyId}}
{"name":"流程测试课程-已更新","users":"测试","tags":"测试","mt":"1-001-001","st":"1-001-001","grade":"204001","teachMode":"200001","description":"已更新"}

### 9.6 课程-再查id
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/{{newId}}
X-Company-Id: {{companyId}}

### 9.7 课程-删除
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/courses/{{newId}}
X-Company-Id: {{companyId}}

### 9.8 课程-再列表
POST {{baseUrl}}/courses/page
Content-Type: application/json
X-Company-Id: {{companyId}}
{"pageNo":1,"pageSize":5}

### 9.9 越权-课程-查16用机构1（期望 403/404）
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/16
X-Company-Id: 1

### 9.10 越权-课程-改1用机构2（期望 403）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/courses/1
Content-Type: application/json
X-Company-Id: 2
{"name":"越权测试","users":"x","tags":"x","mt":"1-001-001","st":"1-001-001","grade":"204001","teachMode":"200001"}

### 9.11 越权-课程-删1用机构2（期望 403）
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/courses/1
X-Company-Id: 2

### 9.12 师资-列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/1/teachers
X-Company-Id: {{companyId}}

### 9.13 师资-查id1
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/1/teachers/1
X-Company-Id: {{companyId}}

### 9.14 师资-新增
POST {{baseUrl}}/courses/1/teachers
Content-Type: application/json
X-Company-Id: {{companyId}}
{"teacherName":"流程测试讲师","position":"初级","description":"流程测试"}

### 9.15 师资-更新（将返回 id 替换下方 teachers/{{newTid}}）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/courses/1/teachers/{{newTid}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Company-Id: {{companyId}}
{"teacherName":"流程测试讲师-已更新","position":"中级","description":"已更新"}

### 9.16 师资-再查id
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/1/teachers/{{newTid}}
X-Company-Id: {{companyId}}

### 9.17 师资-删除
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/courses/1/teachers/{{newTid}}
X-Company-Id: {{companyId}}

### 9.18 师资-再列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/1/teachers
X-Company-Id: {{companyId}}

### 9.19 越权-师资-列表16用机构1（期望 403）
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/16/teachers
X-Company-Id: 1

### 9.20 越权-师资-新增16用机构1（期望 403）
POST {{baseUrl}}/courses/16/teachers
Content-Type: application/json
X-Company-Id: 1
{"teacherName":"越权","position":"x","description":"x"}

