Content-Type: application/json
X-Company-Id: 1
{"teacherName":"越权","position":"x","description":"x"}

### 9.22 越权-师资-删17用机构1（期望 403）
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/courses/16/teachers/17
X-Company-Id: 1

